amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709871455&amp;ssig=WVg49QEm9N&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/S5EORIEqlx08cUPYmv4I010412003o2i0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709871455&amp;ssig=t7TzcQ2FEc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5006739360120866" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
